name: Youngr - YOU Live From Llamaland Studios

metadata.name: Youngr - YOU! (Live From Llamaland Studios)
metadata.description:
And finally... the FINAL DROP from the Web3 album!!! We did it y'all! What a journey. Thank you to each and everyone of you that have jumped on board. The support is much appreciated.

This last tune is called 'YOU!' and it's another one of my live, one-take studio performances. 

Lots to unlock at tell.ie/Youngr behind the token gate, so make sure you head over and have a peak! 

Again, so much love to glass.xyz for bringing me into the Web3 world under their cyber wing many moons ago. We makin' moves out here!
